{"tid":736023,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"迪布尼︰麥巴比？一年前我唔知佢係乜水","createTime":"2018-07-10T02:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T20:10:51.000Z","uid":19889,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e7c78849f36561f91a1e6fa2f95bd7617704d3c5","tid":736023,"uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:46:12.000Z","msg":"比利時在周二將大戰法國上演世盃4強戰，前者球星奇雲迪布尼坦言，在1年多前根本不知麥巴比是甚麼人，但現在這位新星已成為法國隊王牌。<br />\n<br />\n奇雲迪布尼表示之前一直不知麥巴比是何方神聖，直至前季歐聯16強交鋒，曼城在兩回合賽事與摩納哥激戰打成6︰6，最終因作客入波較少出局，自此他便認識這位法國新星。<br />\n<br />\n他說︰「坦白說，在對摩納哥時他只踢了約10場比賽，沒有很多比賽，當時我不認識他，但經過1年半他正效力一支偉大球隊，成為法國主力及出戰歐聯賽事，已成為另一個球員。」<br />\n<br />\n「他已是法國隊球星，在未來15年亦會是，而且還有進步空間，他的確十分危險但我們會努力阻止他。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=8K%2FJt68LUXxfc94keT6z5aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=1e03e682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/UnkemptColossalAegeancat-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FUnkemptColossalAegeancat-size_restricted.gif&h=136d35f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2d8b656542d60365c4bb5da54e5a18aa221ca9a","tid":736023,"uid":186431,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:48:57.000Z","msg":"又係標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed1758db03098e18de4f79dbd69b04be61471a7","tid":736023,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T20:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}